location.fullValue: Yacht & Racquet Club Of Boca Raton

data.description: Very Rarely Available (Original Owner of over 50 years)- this Oceanfront 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Direct Ocean View condo is located in a unique boutique building nestled between 2 multi-million dollar buildings - one of Boca's best kept secrets on the beach. Spectacular ocean & pool views from your spacious balcony, main living areas and the updated kitchen with its granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and bar area. Condo is Turn-key Furnished, Crown molding, generously sized bedrooms, ample storage, 1 car garage parking, Impact Glass. Accordians for sliders. This condo has rare additional access from elevator lobby.  Building has New Roof (2023). Well located on A1A, steps to E Palmetto Park and moments to Downtown Boca & Mizner Park. Don't delay and have to wait another 50 years!
